---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ContactCard from '../components/ContactCard.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="AI Automation | Ice Cap Labs | Wichita, KS" description="AI automation services for Wichita, Kansas businesses — workflow optimization, chatbots, document processing, reporting, and custom AI tools.">

  <!-- PIXEL HERO -->
  <section class="pixel-hero">
    <h1 class="pixel-hero-title" aria-label="Automate">AUTOMATE</h1>
    <div class="pixel-title-grid" id="pixel-title-grid"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- INTRO -->
  <section style="background: var(--bg-deep); padding: 6rem 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px; text-align: center;">
      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem); margin-bottom: 2rem; font-weight: 700;">
        You Need Automation
      </h2>
      <p class="reveal" data-delay="0.1" style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: white; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        Not because it's trendy. Because your competitors are already using it and you're spending 15 hours a week on work a computer could do in 15 minutes.
      </p>
      <p class="reveal" data-delay="0.2" style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: white; line-height: 1.7;">
        We offer it in all sizes. Simple workflows to AI employees. You don't need to know all the answers. <strong>It's okay to be scared. Frankly, I am too.</strong> This is new for everyone.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PACKAGES -->
  <section style="background: var(--bg-void); padding: 6rem 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 1000px;">
      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); margin-bottom: 4rem; text-align: center; font-weight: 700;">
        Three Starting Points
      </h2>

      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
        <!-- SIMPLE -->
        <div class="reveal package-card" style="background: var(--bg-deep); padding: 2.5rem; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem;">SIMPLE AUTOMATION</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-weight: 700;">Starts at $1,500</h3>
          <p style="color: white; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.6;">Email filters. Appointment scheduling. Auto-filing. Social media posting.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600;">Saves 5-10 hrs/week</p>
        </div>

        <!-- WORKFLOWS -->
        <div class="reveal package-card" data-delay="0.1" style="background: var(--bg-deep); padding: 2.5rem; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem;">MULTI-STEP WORKFLOWS</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-weight: 700;">Starts at $3,000</h3>
          <p style="color: white; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.6;">Lead pipelines. Customer onboarding. Invoice-to-payment. Inventory sync.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600;">Saves 10-20 hrs/week</p>
        </div>

        <!-- AI EMPLOYEES -->
        <div class="reveal package-card" data-delay="0.2" style="background: var(--bg-deep); padding: 2.5rem; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center;">
          <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem;">AI EMPLOYEES</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-weight: 700;">Starts at $8,000</h3>
          <p style="color: white; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.6;">Agents that run your social media, track inventory, handle support, coordinate teams.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600;">Saves 20-40+ hrs/week</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="reveal" data-delay="0.3" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 3rem; font-size: 0.95rem; color: white;">
        I use AI employees to run Ice Cap Labs and two other businesses. <a href="/blog/five-weeks-with-openclaw" style="color: var(--accent); text-decoration: underline;">Here's how it works.</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TWO BUTTONS -->
  <section style="background: var(--bg-deep); padding: 6rem 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 700px; text-align: center;">
      <p class="reveal" style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: white; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
        If you're nervous about the future and don't want to get left behind
      </p>
      
      <div class="reveal" data-delay="0.1" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1.5rem; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
        <a href="/contact" class="big-button" style="
          display: inline-block;
          padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
          background: var(--accent);
          color: white;
          font-size: 1.25rem;
          font-weight: 700;
          text-decoration: none;
          border-radius: 50px;
          transition: all 0.3s ease;
          box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(139,92,246,0.4);
        ">
          I Need Agentic AI
        </a>

        <a href="/contact" class="big-button" style="
          display: inline-block;
          padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
          background: var(--accent);
          color: white;
          font-size: 1.25rem;
          font-weight: 700;
          text-decoration: none;
          border-radius: 50px;
          transition: all 0.3s ease;
          box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(139,92,246,0.4);
        ">
          What is Agentic AI? Help!
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="reveal" data-delay="0.2" style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: white;">
        I love talking to people. No pressure. No hard sell. Just a conversation about what you're dealing with and whether automation could help.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- QUICK FAQ -->
  <section style="background: var(--bg-void); padding: 6rem 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); margin-bottom: 3rem; text-align: center; font-weight: 700;">
        Quick Answers
      </h2>

      <div style="display: grid; gap: 1.5rem;">
        <div class="reveal">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-primary);">How long to set up?</h3>
          <p style="color: white;">1-2 days for simple. 1-2 weeks for workflows. 2-4 weeks for AI employees.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal" data-delay="0.05">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-primary);">What if it breaks?</h3>
          <p style="color: white;">It escalates to you instead of failing silently. Plus monitoring + alerts.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal" data-delay="0.1">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-primary);">Will it replace my team?</h3>
          <p style="color: white;">Nope. It handles the repetitive 60% so they can focus on the strategic 40%.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal" data-delay="0.15">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-primary);">Do I need to be technical?</h3>
          <p style="color: white;">No. You describe the workflow. We build it. We train your team.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTACT CARD -->
  <section id="contact" data-speed="0.75" style="background: var(--bg-deep); padding: 6rem 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <ContactCard />
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .big-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 30px rgba(139,92,246,0.6);
    }

    .package-card {
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .package-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(139,92,246,0.3);
    }
  </style>

</BaseLayout>
